		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=100523#p100523" class="postlink">This nametable editor</a> runs on an NES. It comes with tools to pack and unpack CHR and nametable data in a .sav file as well as tools to convert PNG to a nametable given a CHR and palette.

		

